THOUSAND - the series of educational programs which can be used for spelling
           checking and learning of new words in foreign language studies.
           It's a multilingual program for different levels of training:
           THOUSAND - base level   - over 1100 mostly often used words;
           THOUS-2  - intermediate - about 2200 words;
           THOUS-3  - advanced     - words of a particular semantic field.
              Those programs can be used with EGA and VGA monitors.
           THOUSPIC - base level in pictures (preliminary version).
                      Can be used only on VGA monitor.
