About  CONFIG.th file.
            This configuration file is not necessary, but it may be useful.
            There are 22 parameters in it.
         1 - comment's language (the value can be from 0 to 5:
                                0 - ENGLISH, 1 - RUSSIAN, 2 - FRENCH,
                                3 - GERMAN,  4 - SPANISH, 5 - ITALIAN)
         2 - question's language (from 0 to 5)
         3 - answer's language   (from 0 to 5)
         4 - answer's type (the value from 0 to 3:
                           0 - menu,
                           1 - prompt of the first and last letters,
                           2 - prompt of the 1-st letter only,
                           3 - without prompts)
         5 - next 16 parameters are the program's colours (as a rule from
             0 - BLACK up to 15 - WHITE); if you want you can change them.
         6 - one parameter is either to show the time of the session (1),
             or not to show (0)
         7 - the last parameter is either to use the computer's signal (1),
             or not to use (0).
